                                <colophon xml:lang="gez" xml:id="coloph1">
                                    <locus target="#5v"/>
                                    ሐሳበ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ፸፻ወ፻፲ወ፫ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ቢዘን፡ ፷፻፯፻፶ወ፯ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ሮም፡ ፸፻፸ወ፭ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ሰማዕታት፡ ፲፻ወ፫፻፸ወ፭ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ዮዲት፡ 
                                    ፪፻፸ወ፫ዓመተ።ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ፸፻፶ወ፯ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ሐሳበ፡ ሊቃውንት፡ ፷፻ወ፯፻፲ወ፫ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ወዝኵሉ፡ ሐሳብ፡ ኮነ፡ ከመዝ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፬ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለሥልጣን፡ ሰገድ።
                                    <note>
                                        The colophons states: "era of the apostles: 7113 year of mercy; era of Byzantium: 6757 year of mercy; era of Rome: 7075 year of mercy; 
                                        era of the martyrs: 1375 year of mercy; era of Judith: 273 year of mercy; era of the righteous: 7057 year of mercy; era of the elders: 6713 year 
                                        of mercy. All these computations fall in the 14<hi rend="apices">th</hi> year of reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4015Fasilada">Śǝltān Sagad</persName>".
                                        The note contains some inconsistencies. According to the cataloguer, it was written in <date>1613</date>, during the reign of 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9038Susenyos">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe</roleName> Śǝltān Sagad</persName>.
                                    </note>
                             </colophon>
